x. Chapter. Before testing answer next questions:
    Do you want to test as provided test user - jyritamm908@gmail.com?
    or
    Do you want to test as random user?
    or 
    Do you want to test as user created by You?

        Read more below - Administration of Users





--------------------------------------------------------------------
x. Chapter. UNDERSTAND that Test suites are collections of TestCases






---------------------------------
x. Chapter. FOLDERS and FILENAMES


    FOLDERS of TestCases
        FOLDER_Selenium_Tests_Folder
            ReadMe
                FOLDER_Selenium_Test_Cases_All
                FOLDER_Selenium_Test_Suites_TEST_environment
                FOLDER_Selenium_Test_Suites_LIVE_environment
    	



    FILENAMES of TestCases
        TEST_   MF_     Signup_
        LIVE_   Mgnto_  Signin_
                        Create_     Project
                        Access_     Instance
                        Connect_    MF_
                        Recover_    Transact_email



    FILENAMES of Test Suites:
        TEST    Selenium    Test    Suite   Short
        LIVE                                Long






