x. Chapter. USERS ADMINISTRATION in TestCases:
	1. Existing testuser - jyritamm908@gmail.com
	2. Created random user, connects with account [RandomUserName]@peeter.mageflow.com
	3. User created by current tester













-----------------------------------------------
x. Chapter. Advice'is to work with Selenium IDE
    
    First OPEN only one TestCase - Cntrl+O
    Then ADD another TestCase(s) - Cntrl+D

    Do not rename testCases what belongs to a test suite or if you need/want to - then you have to construct these suites again.




    Working with Random Names or Users always first:
        
        in MageFlow:
            Create Project, 
                then Instance 

        in Magento:
            Create Website, 
                then Store,    
                    then Store view,
                        then CMS Page


